---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Parking Solutions — Evium Charging"
  description="Turn idle parking stalls into revenue-generating EV charging infrastructure. Evium manages hardware, software, payments, and maintenance — you collect the revenue."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-evium-dark overflow-hidden pt-20">
    <!-- Background grid pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(45,200,86,1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(45,200,86,1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>

    <!-- Radial glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full opacity-10 blur-3xl" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #2DC856 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <!-- Label -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Parking Operators</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white mb-8">
          Your Stalls Are<br/>
          <span class="text-evium-green">Assets.<br/>Treat Them Like It.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/60 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12">
          Idle parking stalls are costing you revenue. Evium installs, manages, and maintains EV charging infrastructure — turning underutilized space into a recurring income stream. Zero capital required.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact/quote"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-evium-green text-evium-dark font-bold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-sm hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200 group"
          >
            Get a Site Assessment
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 translate-x-0 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#opportunity"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded-sm hover:border-evium-green hover:text-evium-green transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stat bar -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 border-t border-white/10">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 py-6 grid grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-evium-green">500+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/40 font-medium mt-0.5">Chargers Deployed</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white">0</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/40 font-medium mt-0.5">Capex Required (No-Cost Model)</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-white">100%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/40 font-medium mt-0.5">Turnkey — Hardware to Revenue</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE PARKING OPPORTUNITY
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="opportunity" class="bg-evium-dark py-28 lg:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">

        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
            <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">The Opportunity</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            Parking Operators Are<br/>Uniquely Positioned.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            EV drivers need places to charge while their cars are parked — which is exactly where you operate. High dwell times, a captive audience, and existing infrastructure create ideal conditions for monetizing charging demand.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Adding EV charging doesn't just generate direct revenue per session. It increases lot desirability, commands premium stall positioning, and future-proofs your asset against a market that adds 1M+ new EVs every year.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-3xl font-black mb-2">85%</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Charge at Destination</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">EV drivers prefer to charge where they already park — not at standalone stations.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-3xl font-black mb-2">3x</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Longer Dwell Time</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">EV drivers who charge on-site stay longer and spend more at adjacent retail.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-3xl font-black mb-2">$0</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Out-of-Pocket</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Under Evium's no-cost model, all hardware and installation costs are covered.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-6">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-3xl font-black mb-2">+Rev</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-1">Per Stall Revenue</div>
            <div class="text-white/40 text-sm">Every charging stall generates passive session revenue on top of parking fees.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       MULTI-SITE PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28 lg:py-36 border-y border-white/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">

      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Platform</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          One Dashboard.<br/>Every Location.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Whether you operate one lot or thirty, Evium's platform gives you a single view across your entire portfolio — real-time charger status, revenue per site, utilization rates, and remote management without ever leaving your desk.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Revenue Per Site</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Real-time and historical revenue broken down by location, charger, and time period. Export-ready reports for your accounting team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Charger Status & Health</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Live status across every unit in your portfolio. Faults, availability, and uptime metrics — with Evium's operations team monitoring 24/7.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.59 14.37a6 6 0 01-5.84 7.38v-4.8m5.84-2.58a14.98 14.98 0 006.16-12.12A14.98 14.98 0 009.631 8.41m5.96 5.96a14.926 14.926 0 01-5.841 2.58m-.119-8.54a6 6 0 00-7.381 5.84h4.8m2.581-5.84a14.927 14.927 0 00-2.58 5.84m2.699 2.7c-.103.021-.207.041-.311.06a15.09 15.09 0 01-2.448-2.448 14.9 14.9 0 01.06-.312m-2.24 2.39a4.493 4.493 0 00-1.757 4.306 4.493 4.493 0 004.306-1.758M16.5 9a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Utilization Analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Understand peak demand windows, low-utilization periods, and stall performance — so you can optimize pricing and layout across your portfolio.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.594 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h2.593c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.213 1.281c.063.374.313.686.645.87.074.04.147.083.22.127.324.196.72.257 1.075.124l1.217-.456a1.125 1.125 0 011.37.49l1.296 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26 1.431l-1.003.827c-.293.24-.438.613-.431.992a6.759 6.759 0 010 .255c-.007.378.138.75.43.99l1.005.828c.424.35.534.954.26 1.43l-1.298 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369.491l-1.217-.456c-.355-.133-.75-.072-1.076.124a6.57 6.57 0 01-.22.128c-.331.183-.581.495-.644.869l-.213 1.28c-.09.543-.56.941-1.11.941h-2.594c-.55 0-1.02-.398-1.11-.94l-.213-1.281c-.062-.374-.312-.686-.644-.87a6.52 6.52 0 01-.22-.127c-.325-.196-.72-.257-1.076-.124l-1.217.456a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.369-.49l-1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 01.26-1.431l1.004-.827c.292-.24.437-.613.43-.992a6.932 6.932 0 010-.255c.007-.378-.138-.75-.43-.99l-1.004-.828a1.125 1.125 0 01-.26-1.43l1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 011.37-.491l1.216.456c.356.133.751.072 1.076-.124.072-.044.146-.087.22-.128.332-.183.582-.495.644-.869l.214-1.281z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Remote Management</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Restart sessions, update pricing, manage access permissions, and push firmware — remotely, without dispatching staff to the site.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Revenue Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Clean monthly statements per location. No manual reconciliation. Every session time-stamped and attributed to the right site and stall.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 group hover:border-evium-green/40 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-sm bg-evium-green/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-evium-green/20 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-evium-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 21v-7.5a.75.75 0 01.75-.75h3a.75.75 0 01.75.75V21m-4.5 0H2.36m11.14 0H18m0 0h3.64m-1.39 0V9.349m-16.5 11.65V9.35m0 0a3.001 3.001 0 003.75-.615A2.993 2.993 0 009.75 9.75c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a2.993 2.993 0 002.25 1.016c.896 0 1.7-.393 2.25-1.016a3.001 3.001 0 003.75.614m-16.5 0a3.004 3.004 0 01-.621-4.72L4.318 3.44A1.5 1.5 0 015.378 3h13.243a1.5 1.5 0 011.06.44l1.19 1.189a3 3 0 01-.621 4.72m-13.5 8.65h3.75a.75.75 0 00.75-.75V13.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75H6.75a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v3.75c0 .415.336.75.75.75z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">Portfolio Expansion</h3>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Adding a new location? Onboard it into the same platform. Consistent hardware, pricing templates, and reporting — scale without complexity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       ACCESS & PAYMENT CONTROL
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark py-28 lg:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">

        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-evium-dark-light border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-8 lg:p-10">
            <div class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Payment Methods</div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-white/10">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">RFID Card / Fob</div>
                  <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-0.5">Permit holders tap in. Perfect for monthly pass programs.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-white/10">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">QR Code</div>
                  <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-0.5">Scan-and-pay with no app required. Open-access sessions in seconds.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pb-4 border-b border-white/10">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Mobile App</div>
                  <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-0.5">Start, stop, and pay via the Evium driver app — with session history.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="mt-1.5 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-evium-green shrink-0"></span>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Contactless / NFC</div>
                  <div class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-0.5">Apple Pay, Google Pay, tap-to-pay credit cards. Zero friction.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
            <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Access & Payments</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
            Full Control Over<br/>Who Charges &<br/>What They Pay.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Set custom pricing per location, per time of day, or per user group. Restrict access to permit holders or open it to the public. Change configurations anytime from your dashboard — no tech support required.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              Custom per-kWh or per-hour pricing
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              Time-of-day and peak/off-peak rate tiers
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              Access whitelists for permit programs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              Session management and remote stop
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-evium-green shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5"/></svg>
              Revenue reporting by location and stall
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HARDWARE MIX
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="bg-evium-dark-light py-28 lg:py-36 border-y border-white/10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">

      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-6 h-px bg-evium-green"></span>
          <span class="text-evium-green text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">Hardware</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          The Right Equipment<br/>for Every Lot.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Enclosed garages, open surface lots, and mixed-use properties each have different requirements. Evium designs and installs the right hardware mix — L2 wall-mounts for structured parking, L2 pedestals and DCFC kiosks for surface environments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-evium-dark border border-white/10 rounded-sm overflow-hidden hover:border-evium-green/30 transition-colors duration-300">
          <div class="h-56 bg-evium-dark flex items-center justify-center p-8">
            <img
              src="/images/evium-evocharge-l2-wallmount.png"
              alt="Evium EvoCharge L2 Wall Mount"
              class="h-full object-contain drop-shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 border-t border-white/10">
